      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### Imputing Null values"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "tEOUIWKZ2Efi"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Impute Median Value for Age column\n",
        "2. Impute Mode for Type of Contact column\n",
        "3. Impute Median for DurationOfPitch column\n",
        "4. Impute Mode for Number offollowup as it is discrete feature column\n",
        "5. Impute Mode for Preferred Property Star column\n",
        "6. Impute mode Median for Number of children Visiting column\n",
        "7. Impute Median for Monthly Income column\n",
        "\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "0PcNLNV02Jfm"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 52
        },
        "id": "47b12089",
        "outputId": "a709fb5f-a9d9-4501-d21b-fd6cdd3c11a8"
      },
      "source": [
        "# Impute Median for Age column\n",
        "data['Age'] = data['Age'].fillna(data['Age'].median())\n",
        "\n",
        "# Impute Mode for Type of Contact column\n",
        "data['TypeofContact'] = data['TypeofContact'].fillna(data['TypeofContact'].mode()[0])\n",
        "\n",
        "# Impute Median for DurationOfPitch column\n",
        "data['DurationOfPitch'] = data['DurationOfPitch'].fillna(data['DurationOfPitch'].median())\n",
        "\n",
        "# Impute Mode for Number of followups column\n",
        "data['NumberOfFollowups'] = data['NumberOfFollowups'].fillna(data['NumberOfFollowups'].mode()[0])\n",
        "\n",
        "# Impute Mode for Preferred Property Star column\n",

        "##Features Engineering"

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "# 1. Variables de Ratio (Gestion de la division par zro avec np.where)\n",
        "# Note : Nous ajoutons +1 aux dnominateurs pour viter la division par zro et inclure le client.\n",
        "\n",
        "df = data.copy()\n",
        "\n",
        "df['Income_Per_Person'] = np.where(\n",
        "    df['NumberOfPersonVisiting'] + 1 > 0,\n",
        "    df['MonthlyIncome'] / (df['NumberOfPersonVisiting'] + 1),\n",
        "    df['MonthlyIncome']  # Si le denominateur est 0, on garde le revenu mensuel\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "df['Income_Per_Child'] = np.where(\n",
        "    df['NumberOfChildrenVisiting'] + 1 > 0,\n",
        "    df['MonthlyIncome'] / (df['NumberOfChildrenVisiting'] + 1),\n",
        "    df['MonthlyIncome']\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "# 2. Variable d'Engagement Composite\n",
        "df['Engagement_Score'] = df['PitchSatisfactionScore'] * df['NumberOfFollowups']\n",
        "\n",
        "# 3. Variables Catgorielles Drives\n",
        "# Crer des groupes d'ge (exemple de binning)\n",
        "bins = [0, 25, 40, 55, np.inf]\n",
        "labels = ['Young_Adult', 'Adult_Prime', 'Mid_Career', 'Senior']\n",
        "df['Age_Group'] = pd.cut(df['Age'], bins=bins, labels=labels, right=False).astype(str)\n",
        "\n",
        "# 4. Variables de Comptage\n",
        "\n",
        "df['Total_visiting'] = df['NumberOfChildrenVisiting'] + df['NumberOfPersonVisiting']\n",
        "\n",
        "# Affichage des nouvelles colonnes\n",
        "print(df[['Engagement_Score', 'Income_Per_Child', 'Income_Per_Person', 'Age_Group','Total_visiting']].head())"

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "from sklearn.model_selection import RandomizedSearchCV\n",
        "# Assurez-vous d'avoir dfini models_to_tune, X_train, et y_train\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Initialisation : Utilisez un dictionnaire pour associer les paramtres au nom du modle ---\n",
        "best_params_results = {}\n",
        "\n",
        "for name, params in models_to_tune.items():\n",
        "    print(\"--\"*30)\n",
        "    print(f\"Optimizing Model: {name}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Initialize RandomizedSearchCV\n",
        "    grid = RandomizedSearchCV(\n",
        "        estimator=params['model'],\n",
        "        param_distributions=params['param_grid'],\n",
        "        cv=5,\n",
        "        n_iter=50,\n",
        "        scoring='f1',\n",
        "        verbose=1,\n",
        "        n_jobs=-1\n",
        "    )\n",
        "\n",
        "    # --- TAPE CRITIQUE : Entraner le modle AVANT d'accder aux rsultats ---\n",
        "    try:\n",
        "        print(\"Starting fit...\")\n",
        "        grid.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
        "    except NameError:\n",
        "        print(\"\\nERROR: X_train or y_train not found. Please define your training data first.\")\n",
        "        continue\n",
        "\n",

      "source": [
        "from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier\n",
        "from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import f1_score, classification_report\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- Meilleurs Hyperparamtres Trouvs par RandomizedSearchCV ---\n",
        "\n",
        "rf_best_params = {\n",
        "    'min_samples_split': 5,\n",
        "    'min_samples_leaf': 2,\n",
        "    'max_features': 'log2',\n",
        "    'max_depth': None,\n",
        "    'criterion': 'entropy',\n",
        "    'class_weight': 'balanced',\n",
        "    'bootstrap': False\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "dt_best_params = {\n",
        "    'splitter': 'best',\n",
        "    'min_samples_split': 3,\n",
        "    'min_samples_leaf': 1,\n",
        "    'max_features': None,\n",
        "    'max_depth': None,\n",
        "    'criterion': 'entropy',\n",
        "    'class_weight': 'balanced'\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- 1. Dfinition des Modles Optimiss ---\n",
        "\n",
        "best_rf_model = RandomForestClassifier(\n",
        "    random_state=42,\n",
        "    n_jobs=-1,\n",
        "    **rf_best_params # Dploie les meilleurs paramtres\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "best_dt_model = DecisionTreeClassifier(\n",
        "    random_state=42,\n",
        "    **dt_best_params # Dploie les meilleurs paramtres\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "final_models = {\n",
        "    \"Optimized Random Forest\": best_rf_model,\n",
        "    \"Optimized Decision Tree\": best_dt_model\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "final_results = []\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- 2. Entranement Final et valuation sur X_test ---\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"=\"*60)\n",
        "print(\"DBUT DE L'VALUATION FINALE SUR L'ENSEMBLE DE TEST\")\n",
        "print(\"=\"*60)\n",
        "\n",
        "# X_train, y_train, X_test, y_test doivent tre dfinis\n",
        "\n",
        "for name, model in final_models.items():\n",
        "    print(f\"\\n--- Modle : {name} ---\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Entranement sur l'ensemble complet d'entranement (X_train)\n",
        "    model.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Prdiction sur l'ensemble de test (X_test)\n",
        "    y_pred = model.predict(X_test)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Calcul des mtriques\n",
        "    f1 = f1_score(y_test, y_pred)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Stocker les rsultats\n",
        "    final_results.append({'Model': name, 'F1_Score_Test_Final': f1})\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Affichage du rapport de classification\n",
        "    print(f\"F1-Score FINAL (X_test) : {f1:.4f}\")\n",
        "    print(\"\\nRapport de Classification :\")\n",
        "    print(classification_report(y_test, y_pred))\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- 3. Classement Final ---\n",

        "df_final_results = pd.DataFrame(final_results)\n",
